INSERT INTO public.document_chunks VALUES (89, 5, '31d24719225324d036cb6d3a1a701f264643b3936b9a99f0f9da9c25b84efbe2', 'What are "Unique Features" and where do they appear?', 'Unique Features are short phrases that highlight your key benefits. In Google Ads, these map to Callout Assets.
Examples:
"Free consultation"
"Same-day appointments"
"Locally owned and operated"
"Studio or in-home sessions"
When Google decides to show them, they appear as a line of short phrases below your main ad text. They are not clickable on their own, but they:
Make your ad more prominent.
Add extra reasons for customers to choose you.', 'What are "Unique Features" and where do they appear?

